import { StyleSheet, Text, View, Image } from 'react-native';
import crown from './crown.png'

export function Check(param) {
    switch (param.value) {
        case 'D':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 'M':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(50,50,50,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 'N':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,0,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 'S':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,255,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 'd':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>

        case 'm':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(50,50,50,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 'n':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,0,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        case 's':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,255,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>

        case 'DQ':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'MQ':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(50,50,50,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'NQ':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,0,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'SQ':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,255,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>

        case 'dq':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,255,255,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'mq':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(50,50,50,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'nq':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(255,0,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>
        case 'sq':
            return <View style={{ opacity: 0.5, width: 40, height: 40, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,255,0,1)', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}>
                <Image style={{ margin: 2, flex: 1, alignContent: 'center', width: undefined, height: undefined, transform: [{ rotate: "-45deg" }], resizeMode: 'stretch', }} source={require('./crown.png')} />
            </View>

        case 'v':
            return <View style={{ marginTop: 6, marginLeft: 6, opacity: 0.5, width: 35, height: 35, borderRadius: 50, backgroundColor: '445', borderColor: '#000000', borderWidth: 5, borderStyle: 'solid' }}></View>
        default:
            return <View></View>;
    }
}


const styles = {
    round: {
        width: 35,
        height: 35,
        borderRadius: "50%",
        // margin: "-0px",
        // margin: 10,
        // backgroundColor: "#558",
        // transform: 'rotate(275deg)',
    },
    rectangle: {
        width: 50,
        height: 50,
        margin: 10,
        backgroundColor: "#338",
        transform: 'rotate(45deg)',
    },
    cont_row: {
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "row",
    },
    bruh: {
        position: 'absolute',
        width: 350,
        height: 350,
        margin: 35,
        backgroundColor: "#333",
    },
    check: {
        height: "50px",
        width: "50px",
        backgroundColor: "#555",
        borderRadius: "50%",
    }
}
